#MEM id=agents source=/root/yvon/agent-department/CEO/marcus/skills/agents/03-prompting.md savings=4%
M||tx|---
M||prio|md
M||appl|all-ag
M||load|on-request
M||md|qwen3.5-4b
M||conf|[]
M||tx|---
M|Anat|tx|```
M|Anat|tx|1. Role context (1 sentence)
M|Anat|tx|2. Task description (what, not how)
M|Anat|tx|3. Constraints (what NOT to do)
M|Anat|tx|4. sc criteria (how you'll know it's done)
M|Anat|tx|5. Output format (if specific format needed)
M|Anat|tx|```
M|Rule|it|Start w/ the goal, not the method
M|Rule|it|State constraints before asking for output — not after
M|Rule|it|Include one concrete example if the format is non-obvious
M|Rule|it|Never use vague sc criteria ("make it better", "clean it up")
M|Agen|tx|All inter-ag communication rt through mc.
M|Agen|Marc|
M|Agen|tx|```
M|Agen|TASK|[one line description]
M|Agen|ag|[target ag name]
M|Agen|CONT|[relevant memory files to read]
M|Agen|DONE|[specific verifiable criterion]
M|Agen|tx|```
M|Prom|it|❌ "Improve this code" → ✅ "Fix the N+1 query on line 42 so it uses a single JOIN"
M|Prom|it|❌ "Make it look better" → ✅ "Match the Card cp's border-radius and shadow to the ds in Figma frame X"
M|Prom|- ❌ |'NOT_FOUND' }` w/ 404 status when us ID doesn't exist"